Name: Missing bullet
About the game: It is a first-person action shooter game in which the player plays as a special forces soldier，The player is free to explore the surrounding area and needs to survive as long as possible，The player's initial weapons are arrows, shields, and knives，Players can kill enemies or dodge their attacks, and after killing enemies, they can pick up their guns，Make full use of the terrain and weapons and survive! Control keys: Right-click targeting WASD movement The left Shift running Left mouse button attack Space leaping The left Ctrl squats Mouse control direction Middle mouse button switch weapons ESC can pause F Pick up the weapons
